# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:10
translate chinese mills0_df9ab5d4:

    # "At work, I do my normal thing of talking on the phone, setting up meetings for Mrs. Mills."
    "在办公室里，我照常接打电话，为米尔斯夫人安排会议。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:11
translate chinese mills0_09d40539:

    # "She sits at a conference table nearby with reams of paperwork spread out in front of her, working on a case."
    "她坐在附近的会议桌旁，面前摊着一沓沓文件，正在处理一个案件。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:15
translate chinese mills0_c07e23cf:

    # "Once I finish with all the phone calls, I get up to start cleaning, but Mrs. Mills stops me."
    "等我打完所有电话，正要起身打扫，米尔斯夫人却拦住了我。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:19
translate chinese mills0_7a5e3a2a:

    # bs "Hey, I could really use a coffee. Why don't you run over to Java Lava and get a cup for me."
    bs "“嘿，我真想喝杯咖啡。你去‘Java Lava’给我买一杯吧。”"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:20
translate chinese mills0_a7068c0b:

    # bs "Get one for you and Dana as well."
    bs "“顺便也给你和达娜各买一杯。”"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:21
translate chinese mills0_7e389ec4:

    # pc "Sure, I can do that."
    pc "“好的，没问题。”"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:22
translate chinese mills0_256860e5:

    # bs "I want a cinnamon dolce latte. Don't scrimp on the whipped cream."
    bs "“我要一杯肉桂多尔切拿铁。奶油别吝啬。”"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:24
translate chinese mills0_e3febc49:

    # bs "I like it super-sweet."
    bs "“我要特别甜的。”"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:25
translate chinese mills0_1ca80c77:

    # pc "Yes, ma'am."
    pc "“是，女士。”"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:27
translate chinese mills0_a9d77f35:

    # bs "Take my card. It's in the top drawer of my desk."
    bs "“拿我的卡。在我的办公桌最上层抽屉里。”"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:28
translate chinese mills0_1ca80c77_1:

    # pc "Yes, ma'am."
    pc "好的，女士。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:29
translate chinese mills0_2f500a13:

    # "I take the card from her desk and head out towards Dana's desk."
    "我从她办公桌上拿了卡片，走向达娜的办公桌。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:33
translate chinese mills0_2b3b5137:

    # cw "Oh, yes, coffee, yes please."
    cw "哦，对了，咖啡，请给我一杯。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:34
translate chinese mills0_886f8aeb:

    # cw "I want mine cold. A mocha frappe sounds good."
    cw "我要冷的。摩卡冰沙听起来不错。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:35
translate chinese mills0_08551511:

    # pc "You got it."
    pc "没问题。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:36
translate chinese mills0_070ee09d:

    # cw "Thank you! Drive safe."
    cw "谢谢！开车小心点。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:37
translate chinese mills0_3cadb2b4:

    # pc "It's just across the street, I think I can manage."
    pc "就在马路对面，我想我能应付。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:40
translate chinese mills0_278a9a4b:

    # "I walk out and drive the work car across the street to the shopping center where Java Lava is located."
    "我走出办公室，开着公司车穿过马路，前往Java Lava所在的购物中心。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:45
translate chinese mills0_fe248ac2:

    # "I give my order to Tammy."
    "我向塔米下了单。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:46
translate chinese mills0_4e519481:

    # tm "Three coffees today? You must be really dragging."
    tm "今天要三杯咖啡？你一定累坏了吧。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:47
translate chinese mills0_7c4237b9:

    # pc "One's for my boss and one for a co-worker."
    pc "一杯给老板，一杯给同事。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:48
translate chinese mills0_d042a70f:

    # pc "I work over at the law offices across the street."
    pc "我在街对面的律师事务所工作。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:49
translate chinese mills0_fcab54af:

    # tm "Oh yeah? You like it?"
    tm "哦，是吗？你喜欢那儿吗？"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:50
translate chinese mills0_0bffb200:

    # pc "It's not awful."
    pc "还行吧。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:51
translate chinese mills0_cdb61927:

    # tm "I bet it pays better than this shithole."
    tm "我敢打赌那里的薪水肯定比这破地方高。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:52
translate chinese mills0_a8c4ebf9:

    # pc "Maybe? I'm just an assistant to Mrs. Mills over there."
    pc "也许吧？我只是那边米尔斯夫人的助理。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:54
translate chinese mills0_2b4c91e1:

    # tm "You work for that bitch?"
    tm "“你给那个泼妇打工？”"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:55
translate chinese mills0_969673ed:

    # "I am a little stunned at the amount of venom that she loads the sentence with."
    "她话里那股毒辣的语气让我有点懵。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:56
translate chinese mills0_22cb75fb:

    # pc "She's really not that bad."
    pc "“她其实没那么坏。”"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:57
translate chinese mills0_dbed954b:

    # tm "I had a girlfriend that interviewed for her and the old lady just flat out told her that she's not interested in hiring a woman."
    tm "“我有个女朋友去她那儿面试，那个老太婆直接跟她说，她根本不想雇女人。”"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:58
translate chinese mills0_d8d899a0:

    # tm "That a woman couldn't do what she needed an assistant to do."
    tm "“说女人做不了助理该做的事。”"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:59
translate chinese mills0_150baf52:

    # tm "That a woman wasn't strong enough to carry the paperwork and books and stuff."
    tm "“说女人没那力气搬文件、账本什么的。”"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:60
translate chinese mills0_b4678777:

    # tm "And then she practically tossed my friend out of the office."
    tm "然后她几乎是把我的朋友从办公室里赶了出去。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:61
translate chinese mills0_f5e1f993:

    # pc "That's weird."
    pc "真奇怪。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:62
translate chinese mills0_4a631625:

    # tm "Yeah it is."
    tm "是啊，确实奇怪。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:64
translate chinese mills0_c600d14b:

    # tm "What do you do for her that a woman can't do, I wonder?"
    tm "我很好奇，你给她做些什么，是女人做不到的？"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:65
translate chinese mills0_4385024a:

    # pc "Nothing really. I just make phone calls, clean up the office, and type while she dictates."
    pc "其实没什么。我只是打电话、打扫办公室，还有在她口述时打字。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:66
translate chinese mills0_4cf794b1:

    # tm "Hrm, well she wanted a guy for some reason."
    tm "嗯，她不知为什么就是想要个男人。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:67
translate chinese mills0_2b17c9bb:

    # tm "Anyways, I'll get the coffees ready."
    tm "不管怎样，我去准备咖啡。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:68
translate chinese mills0_a9a2d1b9:

    # pc "Thanks."
    pc "谢谢。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:70
translate chinese mills0_88f20fe1:

    # "I give my order to the barista."
    "我向咖啡师下了单。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:71
translate chinese mills0_7353f6dc:

    # "She glances over at me a few times while she makes the coffees. I am pretty sure I recognize her from somewhere, but can't place it."
    "她一边做咖啡，一边瞥了我几眼。我确信在哪里见过她，但想不起来具体在哪里。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:74
translate chinese mills0_08c7e0a1:

    # "Once she made the coffees, I take them back over to the office."
    "咖啡做好后，我端回办公室。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:78
translate chinese mills0_706ebccd:

    # "I hand Dana hers."
    "我把达娜的那杯递给她。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:79
translate chinese mills0_de56f313:

    # cw "Oh God, thank you so much, I needed this."
    cw "天哪，太感谢你了，我正需要这个。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:82
translate chinese mills0_c5031deb:

    # "Then I take Mrs. Mills hers as well."
    "然后我把米尔斯夫人的那杯也递了过去。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:84
translate chinese mills0_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/mills_thankyou2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mills_thankyou2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:85
translate chinese mills0_818c6ce6:

    # bs "Thank you, [pcname]."
    bs "谢谢，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:86
translate chinese mills0_b4ece937:

    # bs "Now you can get to cleaning. I'm going to relax here for a few minutes."
    bs "现在你可以去打扫了。我要在这里休息几分钟。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:87
translate chinese mills0_1ca80c77_2:

    # pc "Yes, ma'am."
    pc "是的，女士。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:88
translate chinese mills0_25119040:

    # "I wouldn't mind relaxing and drinking my coffee too, but I pick up the duster and get to work."
    "我其实也想放松一下喝杯咖啡，但我还是拿起掸子开始工作。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:91
translate chinese mills0_85cd7035:

    # "While I clean the office, I can't shake the feeling that her eyes are on me."
    "打扫办公室时，我总觉得她的目光在追随着我。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:92
translate chinese mills0_897769e5:

    # "That she is watching me."
    "她正在盯着我看。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:93
translate chinese mills0_531ca259:

    # "When I get the opportunity, I sneak a look over at her."
    "一有机会，我就偷偷瞄了她一眼。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:96
translate chinese mills0_367f3b05:

    # "Sure enough, she is sitting in her chair, rotated towards me, staring directly at me."
    "果不其然，她正坐在椅子上，椅子转了过来，正盯着我看。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:97
translate chinese mills0_1bdeed63:

    # "I continue working and try not to let it bother me."
    "我继续干活，尽量不去理会。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:100
translate chinese mills0_9f676768:

    # "It does bother me a little though."
    "不过这确实让我有点在意。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:102
translate chinese mills0_0c2c0972:

    # "Especially with what Tammy had told me."
    "尤其是塔米之前跟我说过的话。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:103
translate chinese mills0_b6d20688:

    # "Had Mrs. Mills just hired me for eye candy?"
    "难道米尔斯夫人雇我只是为了当眼福？"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:104
translate chinese mills0_31f90d79:

    # "I brave a glance at her again."
    "我鼓起勇气再次瞥了她一眼。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:107
translate chinese mills0_e3be7f5c:

    # "She is still openly staring at me, like it doesn't even bother her if I catch her."
    "她依然公然盯着我，仿佛被我发现也无所谓。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:109
translate chinese mills0_e184f093:

    # "Then she smiles."
    "接着她笑了。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:110
translate chinese mills0_516a48ac:

    # bs "Yes, [pcname]? Is there a problem?"
    bs "怎么了，[pcname]？有什么问题吗？"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:111
translate chinese mills0_726bc933:

    # pc "No ma'am. Just, you're staring at me."
    pc "没有，女士。只是，您一直在盯着我。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:112
translate chinese mills0_c0bf0f06:

    # bs "That's true."
    bs "确实如此。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:113
translate chinese mills0_5685fff8:

    # pc "Why?"
    pc "为什么？"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:114
translate chinese mills0_4f2fd266:

    # bs "You're a good looking guy. You know that right?"
    bs "你长得挺帅的。你知道吧？"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:115
translate chinese mills0_3f8cb39e:

    # pc "What?"
    pc "什么？"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:116
translate chinese mills0_464983bb:

    # bs "When I see a young, sexy, masculine man working for me, doing whatever I tell him to do, I get certain thoughts."
    bs "“当我看到一个年轻、性感、充满男子气概的男人为我工作，听从我的任何指示时，我脑海里就会浮现出某些念头。”"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:117
translate chinese mills0_59186732:

    # pc "What kind of thoughts?"
    pc "“什么样子的念头？”"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:118
translate chinese mills0_ee9b49c6:

    # "She raises an eyebrow, and I can almost read her mind as she looks over my body."
    "她挑起一条眉毛，当她的目光扫过我的身体时，我几乎能读懂她的心思。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:119
translate chinese mills0_9453aa03:

    # "Then she seems to push all that out of her head and composes herself once again."
    "随后，她似乎将那些念头全都抛诸脑后，重新整理好自己的情绪。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:122
translate chinese mills0_3ac1f82c:

    # bs "Oh we don't need to get into that."
    bs "“哦，我们没必要深究这个。”"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:123
translate chinese mills0_6b371173:

    # bs "Let's just say that when I see you working like that, it's hard to look away."
    bs "就说吧，看到你那样工作，我很难移开视线。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:124
translate chinese mills0_702cd0f9:

    # bs "I'll be good though."
    bs "不过我会克制的。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:125
translate chinese mills0_9ae62538:

    # bs "There's plenty of work to be done. You get back to yours and I'll focus on mine."
    bs "工作还多着呢。你回去干你的，我专心做我的。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:126
translate chinese mills0_1ca80c77_3:

    # pc "Yes, ma'am."
    pc "是，女士。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:129
translate chinese mills0_0fdc08b5:

    # "I go back to cleaning and she moves back over to the conference table and sinks herself back into her work."
    "我回去打扫，她则回到会议桌旁，埋头继续工作。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:130
translate chinese mills0_f1272a0e:

    # "We don't talk much more for the rest of the day, and when it is time, I leave."
    "这一天剩下的时间里我们没怎么说话，到了下班时间，我便离开了。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:133
translate chinese mills0_9a521cc3:

    # "The whole situation makes me feel uncomfortable."
    "整个局面让我感到很不自在。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:134
translate chinese mills0_0ed7a337:

    # "Mrs. Mills isn't bad looking for a woman her age, but still, it is weird."
    "以米尔斯太太这个年纪来说，长相倒也不差，但总觉得有些怪异。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:135
translate chinese mills0_3829b6ab:

    # "I wonder what I would do if she tried to do anything sexual towards me."
    "我暗自思忖，如果她对我做出任何性骚扰的行为，我会怎么做。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:136
translate chinese mills0_1a3d193d:

    # "Would I argue with it and risk losing my job? Would I report her for sexual harassment?"
    "我会抗拒并冒着丢掉工作的风险吗？我会举报她性骚扰吗？"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:137
translate chinese mills0_943c6ec5:

    # "Or would I go along with it?"
    "还是我会顺从她？"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:138
translate chinese mills0_22eaca64:

    # "Would I fuck Mrs. Mills?"
    "我会和米尔斯太太上床吗？"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:139
translate chinese mills0_421381fa:

    # "I don't really have an answer to that for now."
    "目前我还没有答案。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:140
translate chinese mills0_99d09cb8:

    # "These thoughts race through my head as I drive away from the office."
    "开车离开办公室时，这些念头在我脑海中飞速闪过。"

translate chinese strings:

    # game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:2
    old "This scene will happen automatically at work."
    new "这种场景在工作中会自然而然地发生。"

    # game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:3
    old "Just wait a few days after you start your new job."
    new "等你入职几天后就知道了。"

